✨ GLOW-UP GUIDE FOR WEDDING GUESTS ✨
Bride & Beyond – Episode 2 is here and this one’s for all the sisters, bhabhis, besties & groomsmen! 💃🏽💄

The bride’s not the only one in the spotlight—here’s how to glow without the stress:

🌙 Start the night before – Hydrate, double cleanse, mask up & ice that morning puffiness!
💁🏽‍♀️ Keep the base light – BB cream + concealer + minimal powder = flawless, not cakey.
💇🏽‍♀️ Hair prep = hair slay – Dry shampoo + mini fix-it kit = all-day hold.
💼 Emergency pouch must-haves – Blotting sheets, lippie, mints, mini perfume & mirror.

It’s not just a look, it’s a strategy 😉

Save this for your next shaadi invite & tag your glam gang!
👇🏼 Drop a ✨ if you’re ready to show up and glow up!

The glow-up starts from within! ✨

One of the most asked questions I get as a bridal MUA:
“What should I take for glowing skin before the big day?”
So here it is — my Top 5 Bridal Skincare Supplements that actually work!
From collagen to probiotics, these picks are simple, effective, and easily available in India.

Start them 3-6 months in advance and pair with the basics: water, sleep & sunscreen = bridal glow unlocked! 💧☀️
